  | coauthors =Andrew K. Trull, Lawrence M. Demers, David W. Holt, Atholl Johnston, Christopher P. Price, J. Michael Tredger
  | title =Biomarkers of Disease: An Evidence-Based Approach
  | publisher =Cambridge University Press
